metadata.name: Orchidaceae Clitoralis Bandae
metadata.description:
Animated 3D sculptural work

Theme:
What if human bodies evolved to a single sense? Would these bodies have sexual desires? Would they have genders? Would a spirit such as human soul inhabit these bodies?

About:
This sculptural body is a speculation on the what sensory organs can develop for virtual world of web3. This specimen is composed of flesh while taking on the shape of orchid flower. She has grown tentacles and floating bands of flesh to sense it's environment. While living in web3 her body preserved her sensuality.
